            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>May [the soul] be rested of ...ty?<lb/>? ...... son .......... who
                    died<lb/>..............in the month .............<lb/>..........................
                    year<lb/>....[se]cond of the seven-year cycle, which is<lb/>......leap year, the
                    year<lb/>[fo]ur hundred and eight<lb/>years of the destruction of
                    the<lb/>Sanctuary. Peace.</p>
            </div>
